%section.w-full.text-center.flex.flex-col.gap-3
  %h3 CSVs should be formatted as follows:
  %table.w-full
    %thead
      %tr
        - Teacher::CSV_HEADERS.each do |header|
          :ruby
            bookend = if header == Teacher::CSV_HEADERS.first
              ' thead-s'
            elsif header == Teacher::CSV_HEADERS.last
              ' thead-e'
            else
              ''
            end

          %th{ class: "thead bg-secondary-50#{bookend}" }= header
    %tbody
      %tr
        %td 陽葵
        %td example@gmail.com
        %td akgsdgh3242%($
      %tr
        - Teacher::CSV_HEADERS.each do |_|
          %td ...
      %tr
        %td Name in Japanese or English
        %td Teacher's email
        %td Teacher's password
